  "text": "The data presented in this article demonstrate that different fractions of pre-denatured GAPDH may cause apoptotic processes in neuroblastoma cells. We used the GAPDH binder RX624 to preserve cells from exogenous GAPDH [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . This paper contains data showing the ability of RX624 to affect the apoptosis induced by exogenous GAPDH.",
